{"id":307255,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-中央巡视组进驻福州，众冤民每周一聚举/","date":"2013-08-04T06:18:08Z","modified":"2013-08-04T06:18:08Z","title":"维权网 | 中央巡视组进驻福州，众冤民每周一聚举牌求见未果（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员林仙报道）中央巡视组进福建，入住在福州阳光假日大酒店</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>层。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日早上</span><span>，福州众冤民顶着烈日到酒店每周一聚集体举牌求接见，有的冤民被当地官员维稳，剩下的遭驱逐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>福州冤民有冤无处诉，地方政府信访渠道严重堵塞，而且对上访冤民严加打压，屡屡加以报复迫害。目前仍有十几个诉告无门的林炳兴、江智安、朱祥光、蒋碧秀、陶梅、吴抃、吴发胜、胡淑媛、熊凤莲等冤民，被逼进京告洋状惨遭不法刑拘，至今仍未得到释放，冤民的生存条件极其恶劣，滥用公权害民可见一斑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现在众冤民已经觉醒，自觉抱团取暖抱团维权，只要哪个冤民受到迫害，被拘留、被劳教、被坐牢，都会得到集体的声援和支持！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>福建福清冤民张玲进京上访被拘留多日后，刚好于昨天回家，众冤民借助每周一聚陈情诉冤维权之际，拉横幅予以英雄般的集体声援迎接。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>同样福建南平冤民林贞廉老人病逝，老人上访</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>年讨说法无果，真是举案三尺有神灵，老人死不瞑目！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>福州</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>冤民和著名的福建三网友之一的范燕琼一起在南平每周一聚，集体举牌悼念老人，虽遭百多名国保、便衣的阻挠，仍成功给老人致悼词，恭送上写“党啊亲爱的妈妈，把抢走的财产还给我”的红底黑字横幅一路伴随老人进殡仪馆火化。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span>另悉，有冤民直接上中央巡视组下榻的阳光假日大酒店</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>层查看，已人去楼空，酒店周边也无地方维稳官员和警察身影，显然中央巡视组已转移他处！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xeOrRjYqXxo/Uf2qN_1eiOI/AAAAAAAAmRo/JxUSUWI3GoU/s1600/%E5%B7%A1%E8%A7%86%E7%BB%841.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"239\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xeOrRjYqXxo/Uf2qN_1eiOI/AAAAAAAAmRo/JxUSUWI3GoU/s320/%E5%B7%A1%E8%A7%86%E7%BB%841.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-05w2gVyq2mg/Uf2qMs3l2HI/AAAAAAAAmRY/Qo7mIS6F9T8/s1600/0803_20.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-05w2gVyq2mg/Uf2qMs3l2HI/AAAAAAAAmRY/Qo7mIS6F9T8/s320/0803_20.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-guCM4RxT2Eg/Uf2qNd-ZjyI/AAAAAAAAmRg/ArNhVI9vbDA/s1600/0803_35.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-guCM4RxT2Eg/Uf2qNd-ZjyI/AAAAAAAAmRg/ArNhVI9vbDA/s320/0803_35.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-hg_Rgp0Qz1Q/Uf2qPLAGwQI/AAAAAAAAmRw/bCfnItSxB9E/s1600/0803_45.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-hg_Rgp0Qz1Q/Uf2qPLAGwQI/AAAAAAAAmRw/bCfnItSxB9E/s320/0803_45.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PNxo8PVCAAE/Uf2qP-gE1eI/AAAAAAAAmR4/dKkllxspIBo/s1600/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720130803205819.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"224\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PNxo8PVCAAE/Uf2qP-gE1eI/AAAAAAAAmR4/dKkllxspIBo/s320/QQ%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720130803205819.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cZqgPVb3Mjg/Uf2qSwLlaSI/AAAAAAAAmSI/Zg4ki_GFwKY/s1600/%E7%A6%8F%E6%B8%85.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"179\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cZqgPVb3Mjg/Uf2qSwLlaSI/AAAAAAAAmSI/Zg4ki_GFwKY/s320/%E7%A6%8F%E6%B8%85.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_OV6-HnMzvI/Uf2qR1txjyI/AAAAAAAAmSA/wRMFvH-jIiM/s1600/%E6%9E%97%E8%B4%9E%E5%BB%891.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_OV6-HnMzvI/Uf2qR1txjyI/AAAAAAAAmSA/wRMFvH-jIiM/s320/%E6%9E%97%E8%B4%9E%E5%BB%891.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></